---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>OnlineMarketingCORE - Home</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      
      p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navigation items={navigationItems} logoSrc="/placeholder-logo.svg" logoAlt="OnlineMarketingCORE" />
    
    <main>
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to OnlineMarketingCORE</h1>
        <p>
          This is a test page to demonstrate the fixed Navigation component with
          mega menu functionality and responsive mobile design.
        </p>
        <p>
          The navigation has been refactored to use smaller, modular components 
          to avoid the Astro compiler error "originalIM was set twice" that was
          occurring with the previous monolithic implementation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html> 
